Description: 
        # pywall
        Python firewall framework.
        # Install
        ```
        pip3 install pywall
        ```
        # Using
        ## In another script
        ```python
        from pywall import pywall
        # pywall(iface="wlan0")
        safe = pywall(iface="wlan0").control()
        ```
        ## In command line
        ```console
        pywall
        ```
        ```console
        usage: pywall [-h] [-i IFACE] [-t TIMEOUT]
        
        optional arguments:
          -h, --help            show this help message and exit
          -i IFACE, --iface IFACE
                                Interface
          -t TIMEOUT, --timeout TIMEOUT
                                Timeout
        ```
            
Platform: UNKNOWN
Requires-Python: >=3.8
